### Squash with particle emission

Compressed object \"pops\" particles outward at peak squash.

*[needs: particle system or multiple small entities]*

```scheme
(call-with-world
 (make-world width: 400 height: 400 background: '(250 248 245))
 (lambda (w)
   (let ((frame 0)
         (particles '()))
     (define (draw)
       (world-clear w)
       (let* ((t (/ frame 60.0))
              (squash (+ 0.6 (* 0.4 (sin (* t 4.0)))))
              (h-scale (/ 1.0 (sqrt squash)))
              (v-scale (sqrt squash)))
         (when (and (< squash 0.65) (= (modulo frame 15) 0))
           (set! particles (cons (list 200 200 (* 2.0 (- (random) 0.5)) (* 2.0 (- (random) 0.5)) 30)
                                 particles)))
         (set! particles
               (filter (lambda (p)
                         (let ((ttl (list-ref p 4)))
                           (> ttl 0)))
                       (map (lambda (p)
                              (list (+ (car p) (caddr p))
                                    (+ (cadr p) (cadddr p))
                                    (caddr p)
                                    (cadddr p)
                                    (- (list-ref p 4) 1)))
                            particles)))
         (for-each (lambda (p)
                     (world-draw-circle w (car p) (cadr p) 3 '(220 100 100) 'fill))
                   particles)
         (world-draw-ellipse w 200 200
                             (* 50 h-scale)
                             (* 50 v-scale)
                             '(180 140 100) 'fill)
         (set! frame (+ frame 1))))
     (world-on-tick w draw 60)
     (world-show w)
     (world-wait w))))
```

[VISUAL: A tan ellipse pulsing; small red dots spray outward when it squashes hard, then fade away.]

